WEBVTT

01:40.690 --> 01:45.950
[Speed and Love]

01:46.289 --> 01:48.660
[Episode 18]

02:13.730 --> 02:14.790
More importantly,

02:15.410 --> 02:17.640
we need to find a reliable repair factory

02:17.640 --> 02:19.040
that can handle this job.

02:32.320 --> 02:32.970
Zhao!

02:35.010 --> 02:35.760
Zhao!

02:40.010 --> 02:41.250
Didn't I send you home?

02:41.250 --> 02:42.210
Why are you back again?

02:42.210 --> 02:43.090
I found a solution.

02:43.090 --> 02:43.820
Come with me.

03:17.390 --> 03:19.120
How did you get here so quickly?

03:19.320 --> 03:20.079
Seventh Day.

03:24.650 --> 03:26.079
Let me introduce someone to you.

03:26.079 --> 03:26.760
Mr. Ren.

03:29.480 --> 03:31.079
This is Mr. Ren Guodong,

03:31.290 --> 03:32.730
the chief engineer at my dad's factory.

03:32.730 --> 03:34.540
Mu told me you want to restore your car.

03:34.540 --> 03:36.570
Why don't you two have a good talk?

03:37.600 --> 03:38.320
Uncle Ren.

03:39.800 --> 03:41.230
I was wondering who Seventh Day

03:41.230 --> 03:42.510
Pan mentioned was.

03:42.680 --> 03:43.740
Turns out it's you.

03:44.250 --> 03:45.010
You brat,

03:45.250 --> 03:47.250
you really won't give up
until you hit a dead end.

03:47.250 --> 03:49.170
Where there's a will, there's a way.

03:49.170 --> 03:50.430
Come in and let's talk.

03:52.480 --> 03:53.280
Wait for me.

03:55.480 --> 03:57.340
We need to replace this part here.

03:57.490 --> 03:59.520
See? The front left longitudinal rail

03:59.520 --> 04:00.200
is bent.

04:00.600 --> 04:03.170
And the water pump drive system
has failed too.

04:03.170 --> 04:03.800
This

04:04.080 --> 04:05.480
is quite tricky.

04:06.230 --> 04:08.890
There are quite a few parts
that need replacing,

04:09.080 --> 04:11.300
including the connecting rod bearings.

04:11.300 --> 04:13.300
-How is it?
-Let's do it step by step.

04:14.250 --> 04:15.250
What do you think?

04:24.280 --> 04:25.340
How did the talk go?

04:29.960 --> 04:32.620
Let's go home first.
I'll explain it to you then.

04:34.170 --> 04:35.370
I'm leaving. Thanks.

05:43.760 --> 05:44.940
Does your dad know

05:44.960 --> 05:46.520
they're fixing the car here?

05:46.520 --> 05:47.490
Mu, you're here.

05:48.270 --> 05:49.640
Of course he does.

05:51.130 --> 05:52.260
How did you tell him?

05:53.890 --> 05:54.760
Right after you called me,

05:54.760 --> 05:56.930
I told my dad right away.

05:57.200 --> 05:58.960
I said if he didn't help me,

05:59.060 --> 06:01.130
I might fail the college entrance exam
again this year.

06:01.130 --> 06:02.660
So you threatened your dad?

06:02.750 --> 06:04.340
I'm his only son anyway,

06:04.520 --> 06:06.590
and he wouldn't dare upset me right now.

06:06.590 --> 06:09.190
What if I pull out his oxygen tube
when he's old?

06:13.490 --> 06:15.520
About this matter of Seventh Day, I...

06:15.520 --> 06:16.650
Don't call him that.

06:16.750 --> 06:17.870
Just call him Brandy.

06:17.870 --> 06:19.600
Nobody calls him that anymore.

06:21.100 --> 06:21.810
I told my dad

06:21.810 --> 06:23.190
about Brandy's situation.

06:23.190 --> 06:24.640
I thought he wouldn't agree,

06:24.640 --> 06:26.050
but he actually did.

06:26.200 --> 06:27.570
He even assigned Mr. Ren to help me

06:27.570 --> 06:29.810
and let me clear out some space
in the warehouse.

06:29.810 --> 06:32.000
He's just pretending
he doesn't know anything.

06:32.000 --> 06:35.320
Later I asked my mom to feel him out,

06:35.380 --> 06:36.930
and that's when I found out Brandy

06:36.930 --> 06:38.450
has a personal feud

06:38.520 --> 06:39.790
with the owner of Wan.

06:43.770 --> 06:46.010
Your dad knows that, yet he still helped.

06:46.010 --> 06:48.540
He really is a businessman
with a conscience.

06:48.659 --> 06:52.370
Then I'm the son of a businessman
with a conscience.

06:54.130 --> 06:56.200
Thank you, son of a businessman
with a conscience.

06:56.200 --> 06:57.159
Study hard this year.

06:57.159 --> 06:58.690
I hope you get into college.

06:58.810 --> 06:59.540
Wish me luck.

07:00.500 --> 07:01.430
I'll try my best.

07:40.930 --> 07:41.960
Food's here.

07:43.010 --> 07:44.450
Sanlai, why are you here?

07:44.520 --> 07:46.080
I'm here to bring food
for the little princess.

07:46.080 --> 07:47.380
Take a break, Iron Cock!

07:47.380 --> 07:48.610
Come on, Yang, time to eat.

07:48.610 --> 07:49.409
Coming!

07:49.980 --> 07:51.060
Zhao, time to eat.

07:52.280 --> 07:53.010
Coming, Sanlai.

07:53.010 --> 07:53.570
Here.

07:54.720 --> 07:55.740
What food do we have today?

07:55.740 --> 07:56.740
See for yourself.

07:58.840 --> 08:01.400
You're truly a dedicated
logistics manager.

08:03.530 --> 08:04.410
Here.

08:05.360 --> 08:06.330
Eat up.

08:10.720 --> 08:11.320
Sit down.

08:12.010 --> 08:12.930
Thanks.

08:13.190 --> 08:13.990
Pan Kai.

08:15.600 --> 08:16.810
Stop studying. Time to eat.

08:16.810 --> 08:17.900
Coming, Sanlai.

08:18.090 --> 08:18.890
Are you tired?

08:22.220 --> 08:23.020
Thanks.

08:25.010 --> 08:25.840
After dinner,

08:25.930 --> 08:27.390
please take Mu home for me.

08:28.070 --> 08:28.800
No problem.

08:38.039 --> 08:38.750
Sir,

08:39.090 --> 08:40.159
this question is

08:40.490 --> 08:42.890
(P²)/(2m).

08:44.039 --> 08:45.240
Okay, thank you, sir.

08:56.210 --> 08:56.900
Zhao.

08:58.040 --> 08:58.800
Thank you.

09:00.870 --> 09:02.270
I'll remember this favor

09:02.570 --> 09:03.760
and repay it someday.

09:03.760 --> 09:04.560
It's nothing.

09:05.210 --> 09:06.410
Just a small gesture.

09:18.370 --> 09:19.900
I'll be the one to repay you,

09:19.940 --> 09:20.720
not her.

09:24.680 --> 09:26.010
I wouldn't dare let her.

09:26.010 --> 09:26.940
I wouldn't dare.

09:27.760 --> 09:30.220
I just want to go in
and grab a bottle of water.

09:30.990 --> 09:31.700
Water?

09:33.760 --> 09:34.620
Do you want one?

09:35.540 --> 09:36.340
I'll take one.

09:36.480 --> 09:37.120
Okay.

09:50.440 --> 09:51.640
The car is over there.

10:00.780 --> 10:01.500
Brandy.

10:02.180 --> 10:02.980
What's wrong?

10:05.120 --> 10:07.520
Mu has already been sent home.
Don't worry.

10:11.100 --> 10:13.360
Forget it. Just focus on fixing your car.

10:14.360 --> 10:15.420
I'm hanging up now.

10:35.450 --> 10:37.680
♪ Make it fast, never slow down ♪

10:37.700 --> 10:40.180
♪ Show my transcendent stance ♪

10:40.200 --> 10:41.320
♪ Speeding love ♪

10:41.340 --> 10:42.740
♪ Whether I succeed or fail ♪

10:42.770 --> 10:44.910
♪ I just want to be free ♪

10:44.940 --> 10:47.500
♪ Shining star, heart on fire ♪

10:47.520 --> 10:49.770
♪ The odds of winning are 100% ♪

10:49.800 --> 10:52.620
♪ Make my name be known
throughout the world ♪

10:52.640 --> 10:54.720
♪ You just wait and see ♪

10:54.740 --> 10:57.120
♪ Make it fast, never slow down ♪

10:57.150 --> 10:59.190
♪ Show my transcendent stance ♪

10:59.220 --> 11:00.620
♪ Speeding love ♪

11:00.640 --> 11:01.870
♪ Whether I succeed or fail ♪

11:01.890 --> 11:04.070
♪ I just want to be free ♪

11:04.090 --> 11:06.660
♪ Shining star, heart on fire ♪

11:06.680 --> 11:08.990
♪ The odds of winning are 100% ♪

11:09.010 --> 11:11.480
♪ Make my name be known
throughout the world ♪

11:11.500 --> 11:13.840
♪ You just wait and see ♪

11:32.360 --> 11:33.530
I brought some
late-night snacks for you all.

11:33.530 --> 11:34.490
Come and eat.

11:34.680 --> 11:36.410
-Thank you, Mu.
-Thank you, Mu.

11:41.950 --> 11:42.800
Thanks, Mu.

11:46.440 --> 11:47.560
Thank you.

11:49.370 --> 11:51.170
I'm going out for some fresh air.

11:53.760 --> 11:54.640
Let's sit down and eat.

11:54.640 --> 11:55.560
Yes, yes.

12:22.160 --> 12:23.490
You did that on purpose.

12:23.570 --> 12:24.700
You couldn't find me

12:25.050 --> 12:25.980
and got worried?

12:27.180 --> 12:28.330
I came to see Pan Kai.

12:31.480 --> 12:32.340
Say that again.

12:32.810 --> 12:35.360
Well, finding Sanlai would be fine too.

12:35.500 --> 12:36.960
After his recent haircut,

12:36.970 --> 12:38.700
he looks more attractive to me.

12:41.520 --> 12:43.130
So I'm not attractive to you anymore?

12:43.130 --> 12:44.530
I wouldn't dare say that.

12:55.210 --> 12:56.610
Let me ask you something.

12:57.970 --> 13:00.700
Would you be willing
to go back to Nanjing with me?

13:04.370 --> 13:05.630
When we're in Nanjing,

13:05.730 --> 13:06.890
if you want to run a garage,

13:06.890 --> 13:08.090
I'll do it with you.

13:08.250 --> 13:09.640
If not,

13:10.090 --> 13:12.020
we can open a coffee shop together.

13:15.250 --> 13:16.440
Why a coffee shop?

13:17.040 --> 13:18.330
I just feel it would be nice

13:18.330 --> 13:20.730
for us to open a coffee shop together.

13:21.890 --> 13:24.800
We must choose a location at the foot
of a mountain with phoenix trees.

13:24.800 --> 13:25.970
In autumn,

13:26.210 --> 13:29.470
the golden leaves of phoenix trees
would cover the ground,

13:29.680 --> 13:32.280
and Lightning would run back and forth
over them.

13:32.280 --> 13:33.610
How happy that would be.

13:37.090 --> 13:38.090
Give me a few days.

13:41.000 --> 13:42.330
I'll give you an answer.

14:17.200 --> 14:18.280
Sorry

14:18.800 --> 14:20.600
I can't spend much time with you.

14:21.330 --> 14:23.570
It's the final stage.
I'll be working late.

14:23.570 --> 14:24.660
Will you be angry?

14:37.650 --> 14:38.410
Mu?

14:41.420 --> 14:42.370
Brandy?

14:43.410 --> 14:44.410
You... you two...

14:44.980 --> 14:46.310
Aren't you two related?

14:52.980 --> 14:54.410
It's a secret. A secret.

15:35.650 --> 15:39.010
♪ What was it that brought me to you? ♪

15:39.410 --> 15:41.320
♪ Perhaps it was fate's design ♪

15:41.880 --> 15:45.620
♪ Through all our winding paths,
we always find each other ♪

15:45.640 --> 15:49.240
♪ The storm turned to rain,
and everything was swept away ♪

15:49.270 --> 15:50.980
♪ Slowly, everything becomes clear ♪

15:51.000 --> 15:53.360
♪ In your gaze ♪

15:53.650 --> 15:55.610
♪ I found the answer ♪

15:55.640 --> 15:57.680
♪ There's a feeling so strong ♪

15:57.710 --> 16:00.840
♪ Our story is still unfolding ♪

16:00.980 --> 16:04.890
♪ Waiting for the perfect ending ♪

16:06.600 --> 16:09.050
♪ It all began the moment I met you ♪

16:09.070 --> 16:11.540
♪ There's a pull I cannot explain ♪

16:11.570 --> 16:14.690
♪ My eyes follow you,
my heart chases after you ♪

16:12.280 --> 16:13.250
May I have the honor

16:13.250 --> 16:14.710
of inviting you
to be its very first co-driver,

16:14.710 --> 16:16.520
♪ I just can't help it ♪

16:14.920 --> 16:15.760
my navigator?

16:16.540 --> 16:18.990
♪ When I gaze across the sky ♪

16:19.020 --> 16:21.520
♪ Not even miles can keep us apart ♪

16:21.540 --> 16:24.550
♪ Sweet longing drifts on the wind ♪

16:23.610 --> 16:25.130
Do you know where RX7 is destined to go?

16:24.570 --> 16:26.790
♪ I can feel you near ♪

16:26.820 --> 16:29.250
♪ Feel you're with me ♪

16:27.540 --> 16:28.280
On the track.

16:28.850 --> 16:29.850
And my destiny

16:29.270 --> 16:31.570
♪ Forget the sunsets, forget the tides ♪

16:30.330 --> 16:31.660
is to conquer the track.

16:31.750 --> 16:33.810
♪ Watch the years pass
and wander the world ♪

16:32.360 --> 16:33.210
Are you ready?

16:34.160 --> 16:35.840
♪ You're the only one in my heart ♪

16:35.860 --> 16:38.530
♪ It all began the moment I met you ♪

16:38.560 --> 16:40.690
♪ The road ahead ♪

16:40.950 --> 16:42.950
♪ And every step we take ♪

16:42.970 --> 16:45.590
♪ Guide us toward happiness ♪

16:46.140 --> 16:48.610
♪ When I gaze across the sky ♪

16:48.630 --> 16:50.980
♪ Not even miles can keep us apart ♪

16:51.090 --> 16:53.870
♪ Sweet memories ride upon the wind ♪

16:53.890 --> 16:56.870
♪ I can feel you near ♪

16:56.890 --> 16:59.120
♪ Because I have you by my side ♪

16:59.140 --> 17:01.620
♪ Forget the sunsets, forget the tides ♪

17:01.640 --> 17:04.030
♪ Watch the years pass
and wander the world ♪

17:04.050 --> 17:06.050
♪ We've learned to
cherish each other more ♪

17:06.079 --> 17:08.619
♪ It all began the moment I met you ♪

17:08.490 --> 17:09.849
Have we left Manshi?

17:08.640 --> 17:10.859
♪ The road ahead ♪

17:10.900 --> 17:12.890
♪ And every step we take ♪

17:11.400 --> 17:12.130
Maybe.

17:12.910 --> 17:15.900
♪ Guide us toward happiness ♪

17:13.480 --> 17:15.480
We'll go wherever the road takes us.

17:18.430 --> 17:21.869
♪ We'll both be there ♪

17:33.860 --> 17:36.130
♪ What would I do ♪

17:36.180 --> 17:38.540
♪ If I have 70 seconds? ♪

17:38.810 --> 17:41.540
♪ Would I get a drink or two? ♪

17:42.090 --> 17:44.550
♪ No, I don't think so ♪

17:45.370 --> 17:48.560
♪ I'd rather get on that bus ♪

17:49.090 --> 17:51.780
♪ Find you where you are ♪

17:52.250 --> 17:54.500
♪ To talk about the cloud ♪

17:54.690 --> 17:57.350
♪ That looks just like a kangaroo ♪

17:58.130 --> 18:01.100
♪ And the old man on the street ♪

18:01.440 --> 18:04.270
♪ Sat there with his dog ♪

18:04.680 --> 18:06.980
♪ Asking you if you're willing ♪

18:07.010 --> 18:09.480
♪ To accompany me too ♪

18:14.790 --> 18:15.850
Thank you. Thank you.

18:15.850 --> 18:17.640
Thank you. Thank you.

18:19.610 --> 18:20.920
She's so beautiful.

18:21.400 --> 18:23.090
So, would you like to join us?

18:23.370 --> 18:24.500
Do you wanna join us?

18:25.570 --> 18:26.570
Alright! Come on.

18:26.610 --> 18:27.600
A round of applause for her!

18:27.600 --> 18:28.260
Come on!

18:41.460 --> 18:43.650
♪ What would I do? ♪

18:43.670 --> 18:46.150
♪ If I have 45 minutes? ♪

18:46.700 --> 18:49.400
♪ Would I write a song? ♪

18:49.890 --> 18:52.040
♪ No, I don't think so ♪

