♪ No, I don't think so ♪

19:05.120 --> 19:08.310
♪ I'd rather get on that bus ♪

19:08.830 --> 19:11.530
♪ Find you where you are ♪

19:11.990 --> 19:14.240
♪ To talk about the cloud ♪

19:14.440 --> 19:17.090
♪ That looks just like a kangaroo ♪

19:17.870 --> 19:20.850
♪ And the old man on the street ♪

19:21.180 --> 19:24.020
♪ Sat there with his dog ♪

19:24.420 --> 19:26.730
♪ Asking you if you're willing ♪

19:26.750 --> 19:29.220
♪ To accompany me too ♪

19:35.740 --> 19:37.970
♪ Would you like that? ♪

19:38.640 --> 19:41.540
♪ Would you like that? ♪

19:47.920 --> 19:50.160
♪ Would you like that? ♪

19:50.830 --> 19:53.730
♪ Would you like that? ♪

20:00.250 --> 20:02.490
♪ Would you like that? ♪

20:03.160 --> 20:06.060
♪ Would you like that? ♪

20:17.810 --> 20:18.570
What's this?

20:19.400 --> 20:20.330
Luminous Pearl.

20:20.680 --> 20:21.610
Luminous Pearl?

20:22.130 --> 20:22.990
Oh, fireworks?

20:23.060 --> 20:23.650
Yes.

20:24.480 --> 20:25.210
You light it.

20:25.960 --> 20:26.770
I don't dare.

20:39.250 --> 20:40.290
So beautiful!

20:44.710 --> 20:48.580
Don't you think racing and fireworks
are alike?

20:49.560 --> 20:50.890
Both chase after light,

20:51.440 --> 20:53.090
yet fear how fleeting it is.

20:54.090 --> 20:56.090
The sparks that fall from fireworks

20:56.200 --> 20:58.440
are letters the stars write to the earth,

20:58.440 --> 20:59.640
and also my wish.

21:01.640 --> 21:03.200
You once said you'd be willing

21:03.200 --> 21:05.720
to sacrifice yourself for this case.

21:06.940 --> 21:08.180
Now that you have me,

21:08.810 --> 21:09.920
have you

21:10.240 --> 21:11.300
changed your mind?

21:27.520 --> 21:28.980
The old one is too worn out.

21:30.120 --> 21:31.650
Use this new one from now on.

21:39.310 --> 21:41.200
The pen I gave you last year

21:42.610 --> 21:44.810
was bought with my own performance fee,

21:45.160 --> 21:46.610
not with my mom's money.

21:48.960 --> 21:50.050
Too bad

21:51.630 --> 21:54.030
it seems like
you won't be using it anymore.

22:01.850 --> 22:02.880
How do you know

22:03.640 --> 22:05.240
I won't need it in the future?

22:52.530 --> 22:53.390
I'm so thirsty.

23:01.950 --> 23:02.870
What's this?

23:03.920 --> 23:04.610
Beer.

23:08.050 --> 23:09.440
I mean...

23:10.410 --> 23:11.980
what's this?

23:19.890 --> 23:21.550
You were secretly drawing me?

23:25.290 --> 23:26.160
Just doodling.

23:28.090 --> 23:29.490
Just doodling?

23:33.960 --> 23:35.200
Well, I'm right here.

23:35.330 --> 23:36.730
You can draw me properly.

23:39.640 --> 23:40.640
I'm done drawing.

23:41.570 --> 23:42.530
Why?

23:43.050 --> 23:45.530
Keep drawing. I want you to draw me.

24:51.680 --> 24:53.910
[Pet Home]

24:57.700 --> 24:58.330
Here.

25:03.500 --> 25:04.480
Wait, who are you?

25:04.480 --> 25:05.000
Help!

25:05.000 --> 25:06.930
Wait! You've got the wrong person.
Come on!

25:06.930 --> 25:07.540
Wait!

25:22.520 --> 25:23.700
Just pay back the money for him.

25:23.700 --> 25:25.290
It's only natural
that a son repays his father's debt.

25:25.290 --> 25:27.160
Come on.
He owes you money, so go after him.

25:27.160 --> 25:28.160
Don't go after me!

25:50.820 --> 25:52.480
How could you drive like that?

26:19.860 --> 26:20.790
Why are you here?

26:21.220 --> 26:21.810
Let's go.

26:26.600 --> 26:27.910
That's all for today's class.

26:27.910 --> 26:28.910
Class dismissed.

26:28.920 --> 26:30.850
Come on. Let's go play basketball.

26:31.040 --> 26:32.640
Wait for me, I'll go with you.

26:38.140 --> 26:38.750
Let's go!

26:40.960 --> 26:41.850
Wait for me!

26:50.530 --> 26:51.570
Pass it to me!

26:53.440 --> 26:54.530
Over here! To me!

27:00.210 --> 27:01.050
Pass it to me!

27:19.210 --> 27:20.210
Where's your dad?

27:21.960 --> 27:22.890
I don't know.

27:23.090 --> 27:23.950
You don't know?

27:25.080 --> 27:26.760
You're his son and you don't know?

27:26.760 --> 27:28.440
I haven't seen him for a long time either.

27:28.440 --> 27:29.360
Haven't seen him?

27:29.360 --> 27:30.090
Pull him up!

27:32.440 --> 27:33.370
Let me tell you.

27:34.050 --> 27:35.720
Your dad owes me a lot of money.

27:35.850 --> 27:37.160
If he can't pay it back, you will.

27:37.160 --> 27:38.640
I really don't know where he is.

27:38.640 --> 27:40.050
Don't think that if you don't tell me,

27:40.050 --> 27:41.910
I won't find out where your dad is.

27:43.660 --> 27:44.720
What are you doing?

27:46.470 --> 27:48.000
Let's go!

27:48.330 --> 27:49.590
After them! Don't run!

27:51.890 --> 27:53.100
Hurry! After them!

27:54.090 --> 27:54.890
Stop running!

27:55.610 --> 27:57.010
You brats! Stop running!

27:59.090 --> 28:00.090
Stop right there!

28:13.960 --> 28:14.680
Thanks.

28:17.310 --> 28:18.770
I've always wanted to ask—

28:20.110 --> 28:22.240
why are your shoelaces always untied?

28:22.240 --> 28:24.640
I'm afraid that if I squat down
and tie them,

28:24.720 --> 28:25.980
no one will wait for me.

28:26.330 --> 28:28.640
I want to stay with everyone.
I don't want to fall behind.

28:28.640 --> 28:29.840
So I've gotten used to

28:29.890 --> 28:31.690
whether my laces are tied or not.

28:42.320 --> 28:44.030
If your shoelaces come undone,

28:44.030 --> 28:45.030
you must fix them.

28:46.120 --> 28:46.850
Don't worry.

28:47.200 --> 28:48.200
I'll wait for you.

28:48.690 --> 28:49.360
Okay.

29:07.940 --> 29:09.800
Who did you get into trouble with?

29:12.570 --> 29:13.640
It's my dad.

29:14.240 --> 29:16.640
I don't know
who he's messed with this time.

29:19.290 --> 29:20.160
Who are they?

29:23.890 --> 29:26.490
Not many people in Manshi
would lend him money.

29:26.960 --> 29:28.960
Just ask around and you'll find out.

29:33.570 --> 29:34.920
Let's get your dad out first.

29:34.920 --> 29:36.320
I'll help with the money.

29:36.540 --> 29:37.670
How much do you need?

29:41.290 --> 29:42.770
My shop's making money.

29:43.060 --> 29:43.920
Don't worry about the money.

29:43.920 --> 29:45.120
Just tell me how much.

29:49.050 --> 29:50.650
Having a brother like you...

29:51.960 --> 29:52.620
is worth it.

29:55.600 --> 29:56.400
Brandy.

30:00.350 --> 30:02.410
I can't keep going like this anymore.

30:07.740 --> 30:08.820
In the future,

30:09.430 --> 30:10.960
I want to open a small diner,

30:11.410 --> 30:12.610
adopt two stray dogs,

30:13.860 --> 30:16.260
and just chat with you for fun
when I'm free.

30:17.590 --> 30:18.650
That would be nice.

30:25.730 --> 30:27.330
Let's raise the money first.

30:34.480 --> 30:36.420
[Pet Home]

31:06.000 --> 31:07.200
It's not enough.

31:07.850 --> 31:09.710
I'm still short. What should I do?

31:22.540 --> 31:23.300
Sanlai!

31:28.350 --> 31:29.070
Sanlai!

31:34.060 --> 31:35.590
What are you doing, Sanlai?

31:40.110 --> 31:41.530
[Brandy, I went to pick up my dad.
Don't worry about me.]

32:03.480 --> 32:04.240
Officer Lu,

32:05.020 --> 32:06.200
my friend is in danger.

32:06.200 --> 32:07.860
I need police assistance now.

32:08.060 --> 32:08.670
Yes.

32:09.070 --> 32:10.220
I'll send you his phone number.

32:10.220 --> 32:12.620
Please check his location
and send it to me.

32:12.640 --> 32:13.240
Okay.

32:13.490 --> 32:15.020
I'll wait for your message.

32:33.090 --> 32:34.020
Place your bets!

32:35.160 --> 32:36.850
Alright. Let's go.

32:52.150 --> 32:53.410
You dare show up again?

32:55.210 --> 32:56.250
Cut the crap.

32:58.240 --> 32:59.770
I've brought you the money.

33:00.070 --> 33:00.730
Where is he?

33:11.740 --> 33:13.370
Who told you to come?

33:14.030 --> 33:15.490
You think I want to be here?

33:16.400 --> 33:17.790
Alright. You've seen him.

33:17.790 --> 33:18.390
The money.

33:35.780 --> 33:36.650
Don't push me.

33:37.960 --> 33:39.040
You've got some nerve.

33:39.040 --> 33:40.070
Let him go!

33:41.440 --> 33:42.320
Do you even know how to use a knife?

33:42.320 --> 33:43.610
Come on. Here.

33:43.640 --> 33:44.710
Run, Lai Qide!

33:46.540 --> 33:48.430
Don't hit my son! Don't hit my son!

33:48.750 --> 33:49.750
Stop hitting him!

33:51.370 --> 33:52.020
Alright.

33:52.270 --> 33:53.270
Stop hitting him.

34:20.030 --> 34:20.750
Stop!

34:21.440 --> 34:22.250
You're quite a fighter.

34:22.250 --> 34:23.739
Let's see what's faster,
your fist or my knife.

34:23.739 --> 34:24.489
Kill him!

34:27.900 --> 34:28.750
Brandy!

34:42.370 --> 34:43.260
Lai Qide.

34:44.340 --> 34:46.290
Tell me what you really want.

34:47.320 --> 34:48.650
You gambled away our house.

34:48.650 --> 34:50.120
We lost my mom, our home, everything!

34:50.120 --> 34:51.190
Tell me why!

34:51.210 --> 34:53.210
Why are you so addicted to gambling?

34:56.230 --> 34:57.470
I'm not...

34:57.620 --> 34:59.450
Don't give me any excuses.

34:59.850 --> 35:01.980
Don't cry in front of me. It's useless.

35:04.610 --> 35:05.810
This is the last time.

35:13.820 --> 35:14.420
Let's go.

35:39.880 --> 35:41.600
Are you really going to
just leave your dad there

35:41.600 --> 35:42.400
and let him be?

35:52.040 --> 35:53.640
My dad is really getting old.

35:55.440 --> 35:58.770
I scolded him like that just now
and he didn't even talk back.

35:59.600 --> 36:02.400
I don't know when it started,
but he even cries now.

36:07.260 --> 36:09.190
Do you think I went too far just now?

36:17.080 --> 36:18.940
Come on. What are you laughing at?

36:20.190 --> 36:22.500
What's wrong with you? What's so funny?

36:22.940 --> 36:25.070
The way you were hopping mad back there

36:25.450 --> 36:27.110
looked exactly like a monkey.

36:28.850 --> 36:30.220
You've got the nerve to say that about me?

36:30.220 --> 36:31.260
Look at your face.

36:34.370 --> 36:35.080
Alright.

36:35.530 --> 36:36.570
Stop being dramatic.

36:36.570 --> 36:37.290
Go.

36:44.880 --> 36:46.130
You told me to go.

37:07.260 --> 37:08.190
Are you alright?

37:27.690 --> 37:28.890
It's specially made.

37:29.460 --> 37:31.460
Put this phone against his

37:31.690 --> 37:33.220
and it'll install a Trojan.

37:44.270 --> 37:47.420
[Speeding Auto House]

37:53.630 --> 37:55.500
Why are you putting it in this car?

37:55.880 --> 37:58.810
My car's going to race,
so I need to reduce its weight.

38:02.680 --> 38:04.720
Hello, your delivery.

38:06.650 --> 38:07.480
Coming.

38:10.250 --> 38:11.120
Thank you.

38:14.560 --> 38:15.560
Please sign here.

38:17.690 --> 38:18.440
Thanks.

38:18.520 --> 38:19.080
Okay.

38:26.080 --> 38:26.850
What's this?

38:27.410 --> 38:29.010
You'll know when you open it.

38:50.530 --> 38:51.370
Do you like it?

38:53.580 --> 38:55.980
Do you know
how hard this is to put together?

38:58.330 --> 39:00.660
I seriously think you're messing with me.

39:01.020 --> 39:02.820
I didn't say you have to do it now.

39:03.120 --> 39:05.250
We've got plenty of time in the future.

39:05.770 --> 39:06.650
One day,

39:06.920 --> 39:08.000
we can finish

39:08.000 --> 39:09.850
this great project together.

39:20.990 --> 39:22.590
You want to finish half of it?

39:25.120 --> 39:26.890
Oh my goodness, Lightning!

39:27.450 --> 39:29.660
Did you roll in the mud? You're filthy.

39:30.200 --> 39:30.950
Yeah.

39:31.730 --> 39:32.680
Why are you so dirty?

39:32.680 --> 39:35.240
What should we do?
Puppies can't take a bath.

39:36.050 --> 39:38.530
Well...
we should at least clean it up a bit.

39:42.720 --> 39:44.320
Lightning, drink some milk.

39:47.670 --> 39:48.790
It's my dog.

39:49.250 --> 39:50.900
Why does it listen to you more than to me?

39:50.900 --> 39:52.630
You're even jealous over a dog?

39:55.240 --> 39:56.760
Lightning,

39:56.850 --> 39:58.810
if Mom and Dad split up one day,

39:58.920 --> 40:01.130
would you go with Dad or Mom?

40:01.650 --> 40:03.040
Are you going to ask next

40:03.210 --> 40:05.000
whether he'd save Zhao or Mu first

40:05.000 --> 40:06.800
if they both fell into the water?

40:07.480 --> 40:08.730
Dogs can't really swim.

40:08.730 --> 40:09.990
They only dog‑paddle.

40:10.030 --> 40:12.200
Zhao and Mu can both swim.

40:24.530 --> 40:25.180
Mu.

40:27.140 --> 40:28.470
Go change your clothes.

40:29.920 --> 40:31.180
I'll leave this to you.

40:32.920 --> 40:33.850
My dress...

40:39.520 --> 40:40.850
Which one should I wear?

40:42.150 --> 40:43.350
I'll find one for you.

40:56.970 --> 40:59.030
Help me see which one looks good on me.

41:04.870 --> 41:06.890
Do you think anything
would look good on me

41:06.890 --> 41:07.890
with my figure?

41:13.300 --> 41:14.010
Mu.

41:15.140 --> 41:15.820
What is it?
